  <brief_title>Effect of a Probiotic-based Product on Blood Pressure</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effect of a Probiotic-based Product on Blood Pressure and Other Known Risk Factors Linked to Cardiovascular Diseases.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
